    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, honest condition and has clearly been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior paint still holds a lovely shine, though upon close inspection, you will notice some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light swirl marks from regular washing. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of odors, showing only typical bolster wear on the driver's seat and light scuffing on the door sills. Mechanically, it runs smoothly and has a consistent service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
