      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional vehicle of unrivaled caliber. This specimen has been meticulously maintained to an exacting standard, presenting in showroom condition both aesthetically and mechanically. Every detail reflects a commitment to excellence, offering the discerning driver a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical secondary market offering. We invite serious inquiries to experience this peerless example of automotive engineering.",
      "price": 46500.0,
